==Other contributions== Other areas of Uwe Gustafssons contributions in India is the translation of [[Bible]] into Adivasi Oriya Language for which he developed and compiled The Great and only [[Adivasi Oriya language|Adivasi Oriya]] –[[Telugu language|Telugu]]-[[English language|English]] [[Dictionary]]. He also published a variety of Papers on the [[Paderu|Tribes of Agency areas]] of [[Vishakhapatnam District|Vishakhapatnam]], [[Literature]], [[Culture]], [[Education]] etc.<ref>http://www.sil.org/system/files/reapdata/41/32/97/4132975105911369019384844112542711434/15857.pdf</ref>
